query:
SELECT wb.id, wb.branch_id, wb.year, wb.month, wb.week_number, wb.total_revenue, wb.total_amount, wb.status, wb.created_at
FROM weekly_bonuses wb
WHERE wb.year = 2026 AND wb.month = 1
ORDER BY wb.created_at DESC
LIMIT 10;
